          <div><div class="aurs-vname">Tom B.</div><div class="aurs-vbadge">Verified Purchase</div></div>
          
        </div>
        <div class="aurs-vstars">★★★★★</div>
        <p class="aurs-vbody">"Battery easily lasts beyond a week of daily use. If you only use the sleep function it lasts even longer. Very energy efficient, packed with features. Hard to fault it at this price."</p>
      </div>

      <div class="aurs-vcard">
        <div class="aurs-vcard-top">
          <div><div class="aurs-vname">Aisha P.</div><div class="aurs-vbadge">Verified Purchase</div></div>
          
        </div>
        <div class="aurs-vstars">★★★★★</div>
        <p class="aurs-vbody">"Heart rate and step tracking accuracy are surprisingly good. Comfortable all day. No subscription fee is a massive win — I get all the data without a monthly bill. 10/10 would buy again."</p>
      </div>

      <div class="aurs-vcard">
        <div class="aurs-vcard-top">
          <div><div class="aurs-vname">Kevin L.</div><div class="aurs-vbadge">Verified Purchase</div></div>
          
        </div>
        <div class="aurs-vstars">★★★★★</div>
        <p class="aurs-vbody">"In conjunction with the Aurora app, this ring provides plenty of health and fitness information. Monitoring heart rate, oxygen, stress, sleep, and HRV. Recommended for anyone wanting detailed data."</p>
      </div>

      <div class="aurs-vcard">
        <div class="aurs-vcard-top">
          <div><div class="aurs-vname">Natalie S.</div><div class="aurs-vbadge">Verified Purchase</div></div>
          
        </div>
        <div class="aurs-vstars">★★★★☆</div>
        <p class="aurs-vbody">"Great ring overall. The sleep and HRV data has been eye-opening. Four stars only because I wish the app synced with Apple Health — but for standalone use it's excellent. Will definitely keep wearing it."</p>
      </div>

      <div class="aurs-vcard">
        <div class="aurs-vcard-top">
          <div><div class="aurs-vname">Bruno F.</div><div class="aurs-vbadge">Verified Purchase</div></div>
          
        </div>
        <div class="aurs-vstars">★★★★★</div>
        <p class="aurs-vbody">"Pricing is unbeatable. You get genuine health tracking for the cost of a nice lunch. No other brand offers this functionality at this price. The battery is the real standout — just charge it once a week."</p>
      </div>

    </div>
    <div class="aurs-scroll-arrows">
      <button class="aurs-arrow" onclick="aursScrollLeft()">&#8592;</button>
      <button class="aurs-arrow" onclick="aursScrollRight()">&#8594;</button>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- ── Filters for dynamic reviews ── -->
  <div class="aurs-filter-row">
    <span class="aurs-flbl">FILTER:</span>
    <button class="aurs-fb on" onclick="aursFilter(0,this)">All</button>
    <button class="aurs-fb" onclick="aursFilter(5,this)">5 ★</button>
    <button class="aurs-fb" onclick="aursFilter(4,this)">4 ★</button>
    <button class="aurs-fb" onclick="aursFilter(3,this)">3 ★</button>
    <div class="aurs-sort-sep">
      <span class="aurs-flbl">SORT:</span>
      <button class="aurs-fb on" id="srt-h" onclick="aursSort('helpful',this)">Most Helpful</button>
      <button class="aurs-fb" id="srt-r" onclick="aursSort('recent',this)">Most Recent</button>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Dynamic grid -->
  <div class="aurs-grid" id="aurs-grid"></div>
  <div class="aurs-nores" id="aurs-nores" style="display:none;">No reviews match this filter.</div>

  <!-- ── Review submission form (Shopify contact form) ── -->
  <div id="aurs-form-section" class="aurs-form-section">
    <h3 class="aurs-form-title">Share your experience</h3>
    <p class="aurs-form-sub">Your review will appear on this page after a quick check.</p>

    {% form 'contact' %}
      <input type="hidden" name="contact[tags]" value="aurora-review,pending">
      <input type="hidden" name="contact[subject]" value="New AURORA Ring Review">

      <div class="aurs-fgroup">
        <label class="aurs-flabel">Your Rating</label>
        <div class="aurs-star-row" id="aurs-spicker">
          <span class="aurs-sp" data-v="1">★</span>
          <span class="aurs-sp" data-v="2">★</span>
          <span class="aurs-sp" data-v="3">★</span>
          <span class="aurs-sp" data-v="4">★</span>
          <span class="aurs-sp" data-v="5">★</span>
        </div>
        <input type="hidden" name="contact[rating]" id="aurs-rat-val" value="">
        <div class="aurs-ferr" id="err-rat">Please select a star rating.</div>
      </div>

      <div class="aurs-fgroup">
        <label class="aurs-flabel">Your Name</label>
        <input class="aurs-finput" name="contact[name]" type="text" placeholder="e.g. Jordan M." required>
        <div class="aurs-ferr" id="err-name">Name is required.</div>
      </div>

      <div class="aurs-fgroup">
        <label class="aurs-flabel">Review Title</label>
        <input class="aurs-finput" name="contact[review_title]" type="text" placeholder="Summarise your experience in one line" required>
      </div>

      <div class="aurs-fgroup">
        <label class="aurs-flabel">Your Review</label>
        <textarea class="aurs-finput aurs-ftextarea" name="contact[body]" rows="5"
          placeholder="What changed after wearing it? How did it affect your sleep, HRV, or daily routine?" required></textarea>
      </div>

      <div class="aurs-fgroup">
        <label class="aurs-flabel">Email (not published)</label>
        <input class="aurs-finput" name="contact[email]" type="email" placeholder="your@email.com" required>
      </div>

      <input type="submit" value="SUBMIT REVIEW" class="aurs-btn-grad" style="width:100%;cursor:pointer;border:none;padding:15px;border-radius:12px;font-size:12px;letter-spacing:.1em;margin-top:4px;">
    {% endform %}
  </div>

</div>
</div>

<script>
(function(){
/* ── Seed reviews (your existing on-page testimonials, structured) ── */
var SEED=[
 {id:'s-1',name:'Jennifer M.',v:1,r:5,title:'Does everything — and no subscription',body:'Waterproof, durable, stylish — checks heart rate, sleep tracking, menstrual cycle, and much more. Very comfortable! No subscription needed. Honestly surprised by how accurate the sleep data is.',helpful:42,date:'2026-05-18',dl:'1 month ago'},
 {id:'s-2',name:'David K.',v:1,r:5,title:'Battery lasts for days',body:'The battery lasts several days on a single charge and I love that it is waterproof so I don’t have to take it off. The app is genuinely easy to use. Incredible value.',helpful:31,date:'2026-05-10',dl:'1 month ago'},
 {id:'s-3',name:'Rachel T.',v:1,r:5,title:'Sleek and true to size',body:'It is sleek and looks very high end. I ordered a size 7 and it fits perfectly. The battery lasts for days and it feels great to wear all day. Highly recommended.',helpful:27,date:'2026-05-02',dl:'1 month ago'},
 {id:'s-4',name:'Carlos R.',v:1,r:5,title:'Accurate, detailed data',body:'The ring measures exactly. Very good app that reports extensively. I compared the data with other health trackers and it is all very close. Worth every cent.',helpful:19,date:'2026-04-22',dl:'2 months ago'},
 {id:'s-5',name:'Linda W.',v:1,r:5,title:'Perfect for sleep tracking',body:'I track my sleep which is why I bought it. Battery life is great — lasts the whole week. Comfortable enough to wear through the night without noticing it.',helpful:23,date:'2026-04-15',dl:'2 months ago'},
 {id:'s-6',name:'Marcus O.',v:1,r:5,title:'Real insights every morning',body:'The company clearly specialises in this tech and it shows. Very reasonable price for the feature set. The Aurora app gives me real health insights every morning.',helpful:14,date:'2026-04-09',dl:'2 months ago'},
 {id:'s-7',name:'Sophie A.',v:1,r:5,title:'The perfect smartwatch alternative',body:'Fantastic entry point into smart ring tech. I find smartwatches cumbersome for sleep but still wanted to monitor activity — this is the perfect solution. Undeniably cool too.',helpful:11,date:'2026-03-28',dl:'3 months ago'},
 {id:'s-8',name:'Tom B.',v:1,r:5,title:'Energy efficient, packed with features',body:'Battery easily lasts beyond a week of daily use. If you only use the sleep function it lasts even longer. Very energy efficient and hard to fault at this price.',helpful:9,date:'2026-03-20',dl:'3 months ago'},
 {id:'s-9',name:'Aisha P.',v:1,r:5,title:'No monthly bill — huge win',body:'Heart rate and step tracking accuracy are surprisingly good. Comfortable all day. No subscription fee is a massive win — all the data without a monthly bill.',helpful:16,date:'2026-03-11',dl:'3 months ago'},
 {id:'s-10',name:'Kevin L.',v:1,r:5,title:'Plenty of health data',body:'With the Aurora app this ring provides plenty of health and fitness information — heart rate, oxygen, stress, sleep and HRV. Recommended for anyone wanting detailed data.',helpful:8,date:'2026-02-27',dl:'4 months ago'},
 {id:'s-11',name:'Natalie S.',v:1,r:4,title:'Eye-opening data, one small wish',body:'Great ring overall. The sleep and HRV data has been eye-opening. Four stars only because I wish the app synced with Apple Health — but for standalone use it is excellent.',helpful:13,date:'2026-02-18',dl:'4 months ago'},
 {id:'s-12',name:'Bruno F.',v:1,r:5,title:'Unbeatable value',body:'Pricing is unbeatable. Genuine health tracking for the cost of a nice lunch. No other brand offers this at this price, and the week-long battery is the real standout.',helpful:21,date:'2026-02-05',dl:'4 months ago'}
];

/* ▸ Your REAL total review count. Update this as genuine reviews come in.
   Do NOT inflate it — fabricated counts violate the FTC review rule and risk the store. */
var REVIEW_COUNT=55;

var state={reviews:[],fStar:0,sort:'helpful',pickedR:0,voted:{}};
var TARGET=REVIEW_COUNT;

/* ── Scroll-reveal (respects prefers-reduced-motion via CSS) ── */
var _io=('IntersectionObserver' in window)?new IntersectionObserver(function(es){
  es.forEach(function(e){if(e.isIntersecting){e.target.classList.add('in');_io.unobserve(e.target);}});
},{threshold:.12,rootMargin:'0px 0px -6% 0px'}):null;
window.aursReveal=function(el){if(!el)return;el.classList.add('aurs-reveal');if(_io){_io.observe(el);}else{el.classList.add('in');}};

/* animate counter */
function countUp(el,target){
  var s=0,step=Math.ceil(target/80),t=setInterval(function(){
    s=Math.min(s+step,target);
    el.textContent=s.toLocaleString()+'+';
    if(s>=target)clearInterval(t);
  },18);
}

function load(){
  try{
    var u=JSON.parse(localStorage.getItem('aurs-reviews')||'[]');
    state.reviews=SEED.concat(u);
  }catch(e){state.reviews=SEED.slice();}
  // Add user reviews to counter
  var total=TARGET+state.reviews.filter(function(r){return r.id.indexOf('u-')===0;}).length;
  var el=document.getElementById('aurs-counter');
  if(el) countUp(el,total);
  render();
}

function save(){
  try{
    var u=state.reviews.filter(function(r){return r.id.indexOf('u-')===0;});
    localStorage.setItem('aurs-reviews',JSON.stringify(u));
  }catch(e){}
}

function starsHtml(n,sz){
  var s='';sz=sz||11;
  for(var i=1;i<=5;i++)s+='<span style="color:'+(i<=n?'#f5b400':'#1a1a22')+';font-size:'+sz+'px;">&#9733;</span>';
  return s;
}

function renderBars(){
  var stats={5:0,4:0,3:0,2:0,1:0};
  var sum=0;
  state.reviews.forEach(function(r){stats[r.r]=(stats[r.r]||0)+1;sum+=r.r;});
  var seen=state.reviews.length||1;
  var avg=sum/seen;
  /* Display the store's real review total; never less than what's rendered */
  var total=Math.max(REVIEW_COUNT, state.reviews.length);
  document.getElementById('aurs-avg').textContent=avg.toFixed(1);
  document.getElementById('aurs-avg-top').textContent=avg.toFixed(1);
  document.getElementById('aurs-total').textContent='Based on '+total+' reviews';
  var b='';
  [5,4,3,2,1].forEach(function(s){
    var pct=Math.round((stats[s]||0)/seen*100);
    var scaled=Math.round(pct/100*total);
    b+='<div class="aurs-bar-row"><span class="aurs-bar-lbl">'+s+'</span>'
      +'<div class="aurs-bar-track"><div class="aurs-bar-fill" style="width:0%" data-w="'+pct+'"></div></div>'
      +'<span class="aurs-bar-n">'+scaled+'</span></div>';
  });
  document.getElementById('aurs-bars').innerHTML=b;
  requestAnimationFrame(function(){
    var fills=document.querySelectorAll('#aurs-bars .aurs-bar-fill');
    for(var i=0;i<fills.length;i++){fills[i].style.width=fills[i].getAttribute('data-w')+'%';}
  });
}

function renderGrid(){
  var list=state.reviews.slice();
  if(state.fStar)list=list.filter(function(r){return r.r===state.fStar;});
  if(state.sort==='helpful')list.sort(function(a,b){return b.helpful-a.helpful;});
  else list.sort(function(a,b){return a.date<b.date?1:-1;});
  var grid=document.getElementById('aurs-grid');
  var nores=document.getElementById('aurs-nores');
  if(!list.length){grid.innerHTML='';nores.style.display='block';return;}
  nores.style.display='none';
  grid.innerHTML=list.map(function(r){
    var vt=state.voted[r.id];
    return '<div class="aurs-card">'
      +'<div class="aurs-card-top"><div>'
        +'<div class="aurs-cname">'+r.name+'</div>'
        +(r.v?'<div class="aurs-cver">&#10003; VERIFIED BUYER</div>':'')
      +'</div><span class="aurs-cdate">'+r.dl+'</span></div>'
      +'<div class="aurs-cstars">'+starsHtml(r.r)+'</div>'
      +'<p class="aurs-ctitle">'+r.title+'</p>'
      +'<p class="aurs-cbody">'+r.body+'</p>'
      +'<div class="aurs-helpful"><span class="aurs-hlbl">Helpful?</span>'
      +'<button class="aurs-hbtn'+(vt?' voted':'')+'"'+(vt?' disabled':'')+' onclick="aursHelpful(\''+r.id+'\')">'
      +'&#128077; '+r.helpful+'</button></div></div>';
  }).join('');
  if(window.aursReveal){
    var cards=grid.querySelectorAll('.aurs-card'),i=0;
    for(;i<cards.length;i++){cards[i].setAttribute('data-d',(i%3)+1);window.aursReveal(cards[i]);}
  }
}

function render(){renderBars();renderGrid();}

window.aursFilter=function(s,btn){
  state.fStar=s;
  document.querySelectorAll('.aurs-fb').forEach(function(b){
    if(b.id!=='srt-h'&&b.id!=='srt-r')b.classList.remove('on');
  });
  btn.classList.add('on');
  renderGrid();
};
window.aursSort=function(by,btn){
  state.sort=by;
  document.getElementById('srt-h').classList.toggle('on',by==='helpful');
  document.getElementById('srt-r').classList.toggle('on',by==='recent');
  renderGrid();
};
window.aursHelpful=function(id){
  if(state.voted[id])return;
  state.voted[id]=true;
  var r=state.reviews.find(function(x){return x.id===id;});
  if(r)r.helpful++;
  save();renderGrid();
};
window.aursOpenForm=function(){
  var f=document.getElementById('aurs-form-section');
  f.classList.add('open');
  f.scrollIntoView({behavior:'smooth',block:'start'});
};
window.aursScrollLeft=function(){
  var t=document.getElementById('aurs-vscroll');
  t.scrollBy({left:-310,behavior:'smooth'});
};
window.aursScrollRight=function(){
  var t=document.getElementById('aurs-vscroll');
  t.scrollBy({left:310,behavior:'smooth'});
};

/* Star picker */
document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded',function(){
  var sp=document.querySelectorAll('.aurs-sp');
  sp.forEach(function(s){
    s.addEventListener('click',function(){
      state.pickedR=parseInt(s.getAttribute('data-v'));
      var inp=document.getElementById('aurs-rat-val');
      if(inp)inp.value=state.pickedR;
      sp.forEach(function(x){x.classList.toggle('on',parseInt(x.getAttribute('data-v'))<=state.pickedR);});
    });
    s.addEventListener('mouseover',function(){
      var v=parseInt(s.getAttribute('data-v'));
      sp.forEach(function(x){x.classList.toggle('on',parseInt(x.getAttribute('data-v'))<=v);});
    });
    s.addEventListener('mouseout',function(){
      sp.forEach(function(x){x.classList.toggle('on',parseInt(x.getAttribute('data-v'))<=state.pickedR);});
    });
  });

  /* Show thank-you if Shopify redirected back after form submit */
  if(window.location.search.indexOf('contact_posted=true')>-1){
    var f=document.getElementById('aurs-form-section');
    if(f){
      f.classList.add('open');
      f.innerHTML='<div style="text-align:center;padding:56px 0;">'
        +'<div style="font-size:44px;margin-bottom:16px;">&#10003;</div>'
        +'<h3 style="font-size:22px;font-weight:300;color:#fff;margin:0 0 8px;">Thank you!</h3>'
        +'<p style="font-size:13px;color:#444;">Your review has been received and will appear shortly.</p>'
        +'</div>';
      f.scrollIntoView({behavior:'smooth'});
    }
  }

  load();

  /* Reveal the static summary + verified-strip cards as they enter view */
  if(window.aursReveal){
    var statics=document.querySelectorAll('#aurs .aurs-summary, #aurs .aurs-vcard');
    for(var i=0;i<statics.length;i++){window.aursReveal(statics[i]);}
  }
});
})();
</script>


